OL,7,FBut reports that this could include
OL,8,Fcuts to the personal independence
OL,9,Fpayment (PIP), the main disability
OL,10,Fbenefit, have sparked an outcry from
OL,11,FLabour MPs.
OL,13,FSeveral backbenchers expressed
OL,14,Ffrustration to the PA news agency at a
OL,15,Flack of communication from ministers,
OL,16,Fwith one describing "engagement
OL,17,Fsessions" held by Number 10 as "a tick
OL,18,Fbox exercise" and another saying many
OL,19,Fof their colleagues had made it clear
OL,20,Fthey would vote against such proposals.
