OL,7,FReports suggest the scale of the
OL,8,Fbacklash has prompted a rethink of
OL,9,Frumoured plans to freeze the level of
OL,10,FPIP rather than increase it in line
OL,11,Fwith inflation, delivering a real-
OL,12,Fterms cut to 3.6 million claimants.
OL,14,FBut other backbenchers have expressed
OL,15,Fanger that proposals such as the PIP
OL,16,Ffreeze had leaked out, suggesting to
OL,17,FPA this had been done in "bad faith"
OL,18,Fbefore anything had been agreed by Ms
OL,19,FKendall and the Treasury.
