OL,7,FMinisters insist that reform is
OL,8,Fnecessary given the number of people
OL,9,Fin England and Wales claiming either
OL,10,Fsickness or disability benefit has
OL,11,Fsoared from 2.8 million to about 4.0
OL,12,Fmillion since 2019.
OL,14,FThe benefits bill has risen with this
OL,15,Fincrease, reaching #48 billion in 2023-
OL,16,F24, and is forecast to continue rising
OL,17,Fto #67 billion in 2029-30 ` a level
OL,18,Fthat would exceed the current schools
OL,19,Fbudget and the Government regards as
OL,20,Funsustainable.
