OL,7,FOn Sunday, Health Secretary Wes
OL,8,FStreeting said the full proposals are
OL,9,Fyet to come before Cabinet and urged
OL,10,Fthe public not to listen to
OL,11,F"speculation".
OL,13,FHe told the BBC: "What I do know is
OL,14,Fthe Work and Pensions Secretary wants
OL,15,Fto support people who need help the
OL,16,Fmost, and we've got to make sure that
OL,17,Fthere is a wide range of support and
OL,18,Fthat everyone's playing their part."
