OL,7,FMeanwhile, Greater Manchester mayor
OL,8,FAndy Burnham urged "caution" on
OL,9,Fbenefit changes.
OL,11,FWriting in The Times newspaper, Mr
OL,12,FBurnham said he agreed that the
OL,13,Fwelfare system needed "a radical
OL,14,Foverhaul", but said the Government
OL,15,Fshould focus on helping people into
OL,16,Fwork rather than simply cutting
OL,17,Fbenefits.
