OL,7,FHe said: "I would share concerns about
OL,8,Fchanging support and eligibility to
OL,9,Fbenefits while leaving the top-down
OL,10,Fsystem broadly in place. It would trap
OL,11,Ftoo many people in poverty.
OL,13,F"And to be clear: there is no case in
OL,14,Fany scenario for cutting the support
OL,15,Favailable to disabled people who are
OL,16,Funable to work."
