OL,7,FShe said: "The Government's dithering
OL,8,Fand delay is costing taxpayers
OL,9,Fmillions every day and failing the
OL,10,Fpeople who rely on the welfare system.
OL,12,F"Under new leadership, the
OL,13,FConservatives are the only party
OL,14,Funited in the need to reduce spending
OL,15,Fon benefits ` which is why we
OL,16,Fcommitted to save #12 billion-a-year
OL,17,Ffrom the welfare bill which Labour
OL,18,Fscrapped. Labour must come forward
OL,19,Fwith a serious plan to deliver
OL,20,Fsavings."
